Fliq returns from his joy ride. He finds Brix sitting in front of the 
Ark


"Hey, what you up too?"

"I think I calmed down Bronco. He shouldn't bother us. I'e also been 
thinking about the emotional strain this mission is gonna cause. I 
mean, this was OUR ship. It's OUR dead friends were going to see. 
Remember Gekkidama? We were running to safety with him, and than that 
banister fell on him. We watched him die! This.....if it wasn't for 
the good of the Maximals, I wouldn't be doing it. But are you ready?"

"Yeah...I guess..."

"Good. Let's go find Spears and Striker."

The two go into the Ark and find them.

"Hey. We're taking off in about a mega-cycle. What parts do you need?"
